'''Mishima Shrine''' (みしまじんじゃ) is a {{ill|lt=Mishima and Ōyamazumi worship|Q127948103|qid=Q127948103|1=Mishima–Ōyamazumi cult}} {{ill|lt=Shinto shrine|Q845945|qid=Q845945|1=Shinto shrine}} in {{ill|lt=Kashiwazaki|Q633983|qid=Q633983|1=Kashiwazaki, Niigata}}, {{ill|lt=Niigata Prefecture|Q132705|qid=Q132705|1=Niigata Prefecture}}.

